<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('common/head.ejs', { pageTitle: 'Home' }); %>

    <body>
        <%- include('common/header.ejs'); %>
            <!-- main -->
            <main class="main">
                <div class="main-item">
                    <h2 class="heading display-6 text-center">Golfing at The Groves</h2>
                    <p class="text-restrict text-center pb-5">
                        Cedar Groves Executive Par 3 Golf Course and Driving Range is an attractive nine-hole course
                        located comfortably between Saint John and Rothesay in the shadows of Dolan Lake.
                        <br><br>
                        With most holes having three decks to tee off from, the course offers a great challenge for
                        golfers of all levels. In addition to the two Par 4 holes and seven Par 3 holes, there is a
                        driving range and a large practice green where golfers can sharpen their skills before heading
                        out for a round.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- hours and weather -->
                <div class="main-item large full-bleed" id="hours">
                    <div class="hours-area flex justify-content-between g32 py-4">
                        <div class="hours-wrapper vflex g8">
                            <h2 class="heading display-6">On the Course</h2>
                            <p class="text-center">Whether it's a quick 9 holes or a day on the range, stop by
                                Cedar Groves to enjoy a beautiful day with friends and family.</p>
                            <p class="text-center">
                                Our hours may be updated throughout the season.<br>Check here for the most
                                up-to-date hours of operation.
                            </p>
                            <h6 class="py-2">
                                Monday &mdash; Sunday &emsp; 9<span class="font-xs text-uppercase">am</span> &mdash;
                                8:30<span class="font-xs text-uppercase">pm</span>
                            </h6>
                            <div class="weather-widg">
                                <a class="weatherwidget-io" href="https://forecast7.com/en/45d27n66d06/saint-john/"
                                    data-label_1="CEDAR GROVES" data-label_2="WEATHER" data-font="Open Sans"
                                    data-days="3" style="width: 100%;">CEDAR GROVES WEATHER</a>
                            </div>
                            <script src="scripts/weather_widget.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
                        </div>
                        <img src="assets/images/drone-5.png" alt="Course"
                            class="shadow-2 transition-long border-rad hov-enlarge">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- join community -->
                <div class="main-item large">
                    <div class="join-wrapper vflex g32">
                        <h2 class="heading display-6 text-center">Join the Community</h2>
                        <div class="join-box flex g64">
                            <div class="vflex align-items-start g16">
                                <img src="assets/icons/tee.svg" alt="Golf Icon" style="width: 8%">
                                <h4 class="text-start">The Range</h4>
                                <p class="text-start">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fugit a
                                    necessitatibus
                                    quibusdam non, omnis dolores quas magnam similique doloribus quia.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div style="width: 96%;">
                                <img src="assets/images/drone-15.png" class="border-rad transition-long hov-enlarge"
                                    alt="Range">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="join-box flex g64">
                            <div class="order" style="width: 96%;">
                                <img src="assets/images/drone-14.png" class="border-rad transition-long hov-enlarge"
                                    alt="Member">
                            </div>
                            <div class="vflex align-items-end g16">
                                <img src="assets/icons/clubhouse.svg" alt="Club Icon" style="width: 8%;">
                                <h4 class="text-end">Become a Member</h4>
                                <p class="text-end">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fugit a
                                    necessitatibus
                                    quibusdam non, omnis dolores quas magnam similique doloribus quia.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- video -->
                <div class="main-item">
                    <h2 class="heading display-6 text-center">Experience Cedar Groves</h2>
                    <p class="text-restrict text-center mb-4">
                        Fly over Cedar Groves and experience what our course has to offer. With our magnificent greenery
                        and beautiful bodies of water, our facility is a great experience for golfers of all levels.
                    </p>

                    <video id="myVideo" class="shadow" preload="" controls="" controlslist="nodownload noplaybackrate"
                        disablepictureinpicture="" poster="assets/images/drone-1.png" width="100%">
                        <source src="assets/drone.mov" type="video/mp4">
                    </video>


                </div>
                <!-- reviews -->
                <div class="main-item">
                    <h2 class="heading display-6 text-center">What We've Heard</h2>
                    <div class="vflex g16">
                        <p class="text-restrict text-center">
                            We strive to ensure the highest quality visit at Cedar Groves.<br>See what others have said
                            about their experience.
                        </p>
                        <div class="review-area flex g16 p-2">
                            <div class="review-card shadow-1 border-rad vflex justify-content-start p-4">
                                <div class="stars flex g4">
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-center font-weight-light py-2">
                                    I love this course, the people who work there are friendly the course is great. I
                                    love the lay out and it has helped my my chip game a ton.
                                </p>
                                <h6 class="text-center">Allan Shephard</h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="review-card shadow-1 border-rad vflex justify-content-start p-4">
                                <div class="stars flex g4">
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-center font-weight-light py-2">
                                    By far the most executive par 3 I have ever played. Best greens in the city
                                    and the tee boxes were very well maintained. I took my boss for a quick 9
                                    after work and got a raise out of it.
                                </p>
                                <h6 class="text-center">Carson Dorcas</h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="review-card shadow-1 border-rad vflex justify-content-start p-4">
                                <div class="stars flex g4">
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-center font-weight-light py-2">
                                    Awesome place. Great staff. Ample tee areas. Great putting green. They only thing
                                    you
                                    really need is ice cream!
                                </p>
                                <h6 class="text-center">D Conzie Connell</h6>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="#">
                            <button class="button-1">Leave a Review</button>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
            <%- include('common/footer.html'); %>
    </body>
</html>